tasks: Anchoring Sagittal Plane Templates in a Spatial Quadruped
title:
Technical Report on: Anchoring Sagittal Plane Templates in a Spatial
  Quadruped
abstract: This technical report provides a more thorough treatment of the proofs and derivations contained in a recent conference paper submission. The description of the anchoring controller is reproduced here without abridgement, and additional appendices provide a clearer account of the implementation details.
